message.body: I hope u did not have to go in today?
I did not go into work today.
Good. U been chillin?
Yeah. I should go clean off my car for tomorrow...
Yea u should before it gets bad. Also did u know Toyota is doin a recall on prius. Make sure yours is one that don't need to be recalled
Ah! You cancelled Sunday! Is it suppose to snow again?
My Prius is one of them. Have to bring it to the shop at some point. Thanks for the heads up.
No we are going to Rockville sunday remember.
No...
Yes Hiroko and Yuki party is on sunday at Theresa and Allen's house. It is at 5pm and it is an hour away so no benkyokai plus you will be able to speak with a whole bunch of japanese people
Ah, okay. I think you might have planned this while I was in Philly or something. Do you have the address?
By the way, you planning to do anything on Friday?
No nothing on friday. Did u want to do something on friday?
I'm up for anything. Drinks? It's cool if you didn't want to do anything.
Drinks are fine. I didn't have anything special. So what a way to celebrate with friends. Do u have anywhere specific u would like to go to.
Any place is fine. I just want somewhere to sit down and chill out.
Dinner and drinks or just drinks?
I was thinking just drinks. Dinner is also fine though.
Hmmm okay
Just got an invitation to the thing on Sunday from Julius.
Okay coo. Did u want to carpool with us?
Sure.
Okay
Cleaned off ur car?
Yeah. Had to shovel it out as well.
Whoohoo
Julius is now a mack daddy.
Is he now?
Yup truly
